item.dc:creator: @arham_4 arham 4
item.description:
@arham_4 wrote:

[quote=“Uncalled, post:15, topic:466196”][quote author=arham 4 link=topic=577902.msg4146827#msg4146827 date=1352242562]

[quote author=Uncalled link=topic=577902.msg4146558#msg4146558 date=1352231878]

if i fail so much then why have i helped with servers for the last 4years including Soul-Split and Matrix before it was shut down, you my friend are a complete dumb ass and need to stop leeching yourself and yes it does work in any base i’ve tried in every base no gtfo
[/quote]it does not work with every source. go ahead and try to implement that exact same code into a Delta server running a Bluurs client. i can 100% guarantee you that it will not be compatible. this isn’t even compatible with every Project Insanity source seeing as not every Project Insanity has the donor rank in which you did not explain how to add. if any newcomer decides to look at this, you are misleading them, and showing them how to use poor methods.

And to not tab your code!

if (blahblahblah == 0) {
blah = 1;
System.out.println("Your blah level is "+blah+".");
}

Should be

if (blahblahblah == 0) {
	blah = 1;
	System.out.println("Your blah level is "+blah+".");
}

[/quote]they’re called conventions.[/quote]
Previously wrote that but I figured I’d dumb it down.

if i fail so much then why have i helped with servers for the last 4years including Soul-Split and Matrix before it was shut down, you my friend are a complete dumb ass and need to stop leeching yourself and yes it does work in any base i’ve tried in every base no gtfo

And to not tab your code!

System.out.println("Your blah level is "+blah+".");
}

Should be

	blah = 1;
	System.out.println("Your blah level is "+blah+".");
}

[hr]

Also,

[quote=“islappyy, post:1, topic:466196”]go to the java file named Clickitem.java that’s located in : Server.model.players.packet
search for:

public void processPacket

Under that you will find a } symbol
Hit enter after it once and add this

if(itemId == 13663 ) {
c.playerRights = 4;
c.isDonator = 1;
c.getItems().deleteItem(13363, 1);
c.logout();
}

Moderator :

if(itemId == #### ) { c.playerRights = @; c.getItems().deleteItem(####, 1); c.logout(); }

Premium:

if(itemId == #### ) { c.playerRights = @; c.isPremium = 1; c.isDonator = 1; c.getItems().deleteItem(####, 1); c.logout(); } [/quote]

[quote=“islappyy, post:1, topic:466196”] c.logout(); [/quote]
